title: Doing Stress Cartwheels
description:
Domonique and Charlie get into the downfall of Tom Brady and Aaron Rodgers before discussing LeBron James and Lakers, Bryce Harper, and our weekly bets. After that, Ashley Foxworth hands out a few roses and thorns after a weekend full of socializing.
